---
// privacy.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="FORGOR - Privacy Policy">
    <Header />
    
    <main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center p-8 text-white bg-purple-DEFAULT">
        <section class="max-w-3xl bg-purple-800 p-8 md:p-12 text-left">
            <h1 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display mb-8 text-center">
                YOUR PRIVACY MATTERS
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90">
                We keep it simple: your data is yours. Here’s what that means.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">What We Collect</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90 space-y-2">
                <li>Account info: email, username, hashed password.</li>
                <li>Uploads: files, metadata, and AI-generated tags.</li>
                <li>Usage data: anonymous stats to improve performance.</li>
                <li>Interaction data: clicks and views to refine recommendations.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">How We Use It</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90 space-y-2">
                <li>Run core features like search and summaries.</li>
                <li>Make results and digests more relevant.</li>
                <li>Send you account updates and optional emails.</li>
                <li>Keep accounts secure and block fraud.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">Sharing</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90">
                We don’t sell your data. We only use trusted third-party tools (hosting, email, AI services) to keep FORGOR running. We may share info if required by law.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">Security</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90">
                Data is encrypted, passwords are hashed, and access is restricted. We review our security practices regularly.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">Your Choices</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90 space-y-2">
                <li>Export your data anytime.</li>
                <li>Update account info in settings.</li>
                <li>Delete your account to remove all data.</li>
                <li>Unsubscribe from emails in the footer.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">Updates</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90">
                If we change this policy, we’ll post it here and notify you if it’s major.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT text-2xl font-display mb-4 mt-8">Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90">
                Questions? Email <a href="mailto:nikhil@forgor.space" class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT hover:underline">nikhil@forgor.space</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <Footer />
</Layout>
